{
  "component": "Indicator",
  "kebab": "indicator",
  "aliasOf": null,
  "title": "Indicator",
  "description": {
    "en": "Activity spinner for indefinite, short-duration waits (loading, network fetching). Always animated; has no progress value.",
    "ja": "不定・短時間の待機用スピナー（ローディング、ネットワーク取得）。常にアニメーション、進捗値なし。"
  },
  "usage": {
    "en": "Use Indicator to signal 'something is happening' when you don't know the duration. For progress percent use Progress. Combine with `visibility` binding to show only while loading.",
    "ja": "所要時間不明で「何かが進行中」だと示したいときに使う。進捗 % が分かるなら Progress。`visibility` binding と組み合わせてロード中のみ表示する。"
  },
  "aliasNotice": null,
